      "text": "PATH is an [[Esoteric Programming Language]] that combines the simplicity of [[Brainfuck Language]] with the fun of [[Befunge Language]].  It has the same memory model and memory-manipulating instructions as [[Brainfuck Language]], but contains a few extra instructions that allow for two-dimensional control flow and thus executable [[Ascii Art]].",
